{"tid":1908040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅致光：反送中抗爭令失業率致5%","createTime":"2020-03-03T04:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T05:13:38.000Z","uid":42188,"like":10,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"56492c6b51fc2c0b4490e8c664fbfd7e48f85c36","tid":1908040,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:04:51.000Z","msg":"可致命的武漢肺炎開始打擊本港經濟，多間公司均裁員或變相減薪。<span style=\"color: red;\">自詡IQ高達160的勞工及福利局長羅致光在電台節目稱，2003年前香港未有自由行，以本地消費為主，但自去年中反送中抗爭至今，每日失去10多萬訪港遊客，令飲食、零售等行業大受影響。他很難估計失業率會否高於2003年沙士時的8.7%，但4至5%「走唔甩」</span>。他又指，關愛基金本月將開會商討向非永久居民「派發」1萬元的細節，資產審查申請人時會盡量寬鬆，形容這是政府期望的工作方向。"},{"pid":"917f8cb79de3a559af2c1d3044a92a6167e0accd","tid":1908040,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"嘩 咁撚多啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66303d9b0fbe0d24ed0e6d03d258dd7089ea9ea","tid":1908040,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:05:50.000Z","msg":"改口了<br />\n反送中的錯"},{"pid":"fa5ce24f4fea39be2ed650965f82243d31bb16a2","tid":1908040,"uid":82628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:05:56.000Z","msg":"一日最衰都係佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942466bd7a4ecb1919f75d0ee47d4fa511992c6c","tid":1908040,"uid":144626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"5%就嘈生晒<br />\n當年8%都未嘈喇屌你老母"},{"pid":"de547179565a2c3ca26af8ceac31d3103206be1a","tid":1908040,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"5%咁低咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0acd6d3b51733f2a5a7e1310249632de3e0b3d4","tid":1908040,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de547179565a2c3ca26af8ceac31d3103206be1a","tid":1908040,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"5%咁低咋<img sr